videos.description: Cullen Neal turns defense in to offense with a nice up-and-under layup for Saint Mary's.
videos.headline: Neal gets the steal and acrobatic score

videos.description: Emmett Narr attacks the rim and gets the layup to fall through contact for the Cougars.
videos.headline: Saint Mary's Narr drops in and-1 layup

videos.description: Jock Landale is a smooth operator in the paint for the Gaels, knocking down the turnaround hook.
videos.headline: Saint Mary's Landale displays smooth moves in the paint

videos.description: Jock Landale continues to dominate taking the lob from Emmett Narr and slamming it home for Saint Mary's.
videos.headline: Landale throws down alley-oop
